name: AccountsReceivableFactoring
0:
”Alexa, open accounts receivable factoring.”
”What is my factoring rate?”
”How much funding will I receive?”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: accounts receivable factoring
des: Using accounts receivable factoring, you are able to tell Alexa how much your invoice is for and what your factoring rate is. Alexa will then calculate the factoring fees for you and tell you how much you can expect to get funded for your invoices. You will need to now your factoring rate in order to use this skill. In general, DSA Factors offers factoring rates between 2-5%, to get a quote, please give DSA Factors a call at 773-248-9000. You can learn more about accounts receivable factoring by visiting DSAFactors.com
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
